(40, 4, 23, 40, 11, 5, 5, 'healing all manner of sickness', 'Healing and Preaching Connection', 'Both passages emphasize Jesus'' ministry of healing and preaching. Matthew 4:23 mentions healing all manner of sickness, while Matthew 11:5 lists specific healings and the preaching of the gospel.', 'theme', 0.377, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
